reviewText:
I bought this for a friend of mine & he said he was very satisfied with it.  He builds scale models of
WWII Aircraft & he was particularly interested in the cockpit detail.

Awesome machine
History buffs be welcome the machine itself takes over the film because it is that good.
Film ordinary but hey history how ordinary is that but good enough to watch many times.
Which this one veiwer will do
It is a good collecters item.
Enjoy!
